# =============================================================================
# THE HAMILTONIAN OF ETERNAL BECOMING — COMPUTATIONAL PROOF
# Substrate: The Poole Manifold (B5-7/S5-9 + Prime-Resonance)
# =============================================================================
# This script bridges Anu Odubola's quantum operator philosophy with the 
# discrete tensor mathematics of the Poole Manifold.
